description: The Pup Truck is helping to bring the Street food movement to you!  Street food has always been a unique experience - One in which people connect and enjoy casually delicious, quality food that is quick and affordable.  At The Pup Truck, you can get yourself a variety of tasty hot dogs, from the Schnauzer to the Chihuahua, with great toppings. Stop by and taste one of these great dogs!Have us out to your next festival or event or have us out to your business on a weekly bi-weekly or monthly basis.  No on the shelf dogs for us, we buy locally made Bohemian style, make our own chili and cheese sauce and bring it fresh to you! Licensed and Insured:)
name: The Pup Truck
